#GEOM based on ([Cal Sans UI & Cal Sans Text](https://github.com/calcom/sans-ui))
tag: "GEOM"
display_name: "Geometric Form"
min_value: 0 
default_value:  0
max_value: 100
precision: 1
fallback {
  name: "Default"
  value: 0.00
}
